    <item>
      <title>14.15 Letters</title>
      <link>https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/14-15-letters/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/14-15-letters/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 09:48:23 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;main id="wp--skip-link--target" class="wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"&gt; &lt;div class="wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"&gt;&lt;h1 class="wp-block-post-title"&gt;14.15 Letters&lt;/h1&gt;   &lt;div style="height:1px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;/div&gt;   &lt;div class="entry-content wp-block-post-content is-layout-constrained wp-block-post-content-is-layout-constrained"&gt; &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;sub&gt;T/N: I know not the best way to format this chapter&amp;#8230;.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" /&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;(&lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/14-14-starvation/"&gt;Previous Chapter&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Dear Maomao-san,&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-left wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;With regards to Zhizi-san, she can finally eat the normal amount of food. Now that she can eat properly, she has calmed down a lot and has evolved from a stray dog to a puppy-in-training.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-left wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;At first, I thought an impossible child has been sent in, but now that she is eating well, she seems obedient. Although, I believe that is a given since she’s eating what Yao-sama personally cooked herself.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-left wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Lately, she does not just use the knife, but she can even cook now, but I personally would offer to do all the cooking for her.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-left wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Also, Yao-sama is finally receptive to moving out, so we’re in the middle of looking for property. Since we still have Zhizi-san’s matter, I believe we won’t be leaving Rakan-sama’s residence considering public order until after the new year, but it is a big step.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-left wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;We’ll inform you once we’ve decided on a place.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-left wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;&lt;span class="uppercase"&gt;F&lt;/span&gt;rom En’en.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;En’en is still the same&lt;/em&gt;, Maomao thought.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Yao wants to be independent. Would she invite En’en to where she would be moving to?&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;To Maomao,&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Long time no seee. You were my reference for my job so I thought I should send you a letter, and so I did.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Yup, it’s pretty terrible at the site. All the villagers are clamouring to leave as soon as possible. It’s quite heart-wrenching. You ask if Yo is alright? Yup, she’s pretty worn out so she’ll be coming back for now. She still wants to keep going, but it should be fine for her to spend the new year with her family at least, riiight?&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Court Physician Lao, was it? He’s a great person. He was receptive to the idea of having Yo return for now. What an understanding grandpa.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;When Yo gets back, I’ll leave her to you. Unless Maomao isn’t okay with it, then I won’t send her your way. I’ll be coming back with her, so an inn, please. The court physicians will prepare the necessary expenses for this at least.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Also, I have a question. Would you happen to know a place near the capital that has a lot of cows and horses?&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sup&gt;From Kokuyou&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;“So Yo-san and Kokuyou are coming back.”&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Yo must be finding the work tough. She will have to stay in the capital until she recovers her spirit like Kokuyou said.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Even so, what was that about cows and horses? &lt;em&gt;Red Plum Mansion fits the criteria, so it should be fine if I introduce that place to him,&lt;/em&gt; she thought as she set down the letter from Kokuyou.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Maomao-san, Maomao-san,&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Why, Chue-san shall showcase a special product to you.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Now, come, come, please take a look. Chue-san will showcase each and every item that won over her husband. There are easy-to-understand illustrations included&amp;#8211;&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Maomao ripped up the letter without reading the rest and dumped it into the brazier.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Dear Sis,&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Taking custody of Hao-sama’s daughter under the Moon Prince’s orders was fine, but to think that you were involved…&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;She has such a beautiful face it’s a waste. Even though her looks won’t bring a nation to ruin, with her pedigree and the bare minimum of education, she could have gone on to become a middle-ranking consort at least.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Zhizi-san’s height is eight &lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;sun &lt;/sub&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;shorter than girls her age, and while she is steadily putting on weight, it is not yet enough.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Also regarding her speech, it doesn’t seem like she has had much contact with the outside world. No matter how tenderly the young lady was raised, if her mother and wet nurse spoke to her properly, her language faculties could have developed a little more.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Hahaha, seems like the mother treated her daughter as a doll or a pet. It actually irks me. A child uneducated is no different from an animal.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Regarding Hao-sama, I am aware of him. I heard a rumour that he roused the anger of the emperor the other day, but I wonder if that’s true. That person would be quite capable of it.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;The empress dowager’s relative he may be, but he’s hopeless. That beautiful and youthful face is wasted on him.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Ah, his three sons got their good-looking faces from their father, but all of them are suited to be married into families as son-in-laws. Their personalities don’t resemble their father&amp;#8217;s. They’re good at being aides, and are not the type to want to show off.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;That is what I’ve heard though…&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;I’ve heard all of sorts of rumours, but I am keenly aware that I need to look into them properly.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Hao-sama’s third son does come to visit quite often. He says he’s here to visit his younger sister and he delivers cow’s milk each time. Zhizi-san also appears happy for the third son’s visit. She looks like a dog wagging its tail.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;He seems to adore her, saying that his younger sister is smart, but no matter how I see it, it’s favouritism. His eyes are blurry.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;If that’s how he’s going to be, I wanted to tell him that he should have given her proper food and raised her, but it’s not beautiful to interfere in a family that has no relation to you. And not like our family is one to talk about others.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;When I tried to gently dissuade him from coming too often, Brother started to hand out vegetables he’d grown and got cow’s milk in exchange. Moreover, he started to make dairy products that he learnt from the western capital. It is handy in various way to have Brother here, but I want him to stop expanding his field.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Also, Maomao, I have a request for you.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;I am working very hard because of this incident that&amp;#8217;s related to you, so can you listen to a request of mine?&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;You seem to have some connection to a wheat farmer and I heard that you can purchase wheat at low prices. Can you introduce them to me?&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Mm, if you asking why, a ship carrying wheat sank because of a variety of reasons.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;If you can write me one letter of introduction, that will settle the matter with Zhizi-san. There will be no debts between us with that.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;From Rahan&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;To Rahan,&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;No.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Maomao&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Maomao immediately wrote him a reply.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Maomao dear,&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Are you eating well? I am eating well, so rest assured.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;On top of three meals a day, Gu’en-san gives me snacks every time. It’s a mystery, though. How does he prepare so many colourful snacks?&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;I have heard from Liu-san. It seems like Maomao is thinking that because you have never caught smallpox, you won’t ever be sent to the site.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Despite Lao-san’s appearance, his medical skill is on par with Liu-san. He makes good decisions too. You can leave it to him.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;If you were to ever catch smallpox, I will take the responsibility to nurse you back to health. Should that time come, I will probably catch smallpox too, won’t I?&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Also, it seems like Hao-sama’s daughter has come under the Moon Prince’s orders, but I will be visiting roughly every half a month.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;I was told that I could commute to the inner palace from the residence every day, but now is not the time. I cannot leave Gu’en-san alone. Sorry for that.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;From Luomen&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;The quack doctor’s snack procurement channel was certainly a mystery. It may be the inner palace, but you can consider it an enigma how he keeps a steady supply of this many snacks while rarely leaving the inner palace.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;However, this wasn’t a puzzle for her to solve, so she set it aside.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;With regards to the reason why Luomen couldn’t easily return, Maomao wondered if it was to keep the consorts in check rather than for their pregnancies.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;The consorts could poison one another.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Should anything happen, the quack doctor probably wouldn’t be able to deal with it alone.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;To Maomao,&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Hey, is Kokuyou coming back any time soon?&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Is he? Is he?&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;He’ll be back by the new year, right?&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;When he’s not here, I’m beside myself with worry. To tell you how depressed I am, it’s to the point where the courtesans of Verdigris Mansion are coming to console me.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;You got that? Let me know as soon as you get news of Kokuyou’s return.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Also, you have another letter. I’ve enclosed it.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;From Sazen&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;There was another letter inside. The slightly poor quality paper wasn’t scented. The characters were clumsy yet written with care.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;To Maomao,&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;It’s gotten cold, hasn’t it?&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;I am doing my best. Somehow, a lot of people want to marry even someone like me.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;Everyone reacted when I told them I come from the inner palace. It really is an amazing place.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;I also want to visit Verdigris Mansion once, but it’s impossible since I will need to save up years of my wages.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;See you. Once I get nice paper, I’ll write you again.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;sub&gt;From Xiaolan&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;“&amp;#8230;Like I said, write down your address. I can’t send you a reply otherwise.”&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;Maomao placed the letter into her box of letters.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" /&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;sub&gt;T/N: Someone needs to connect Xiaolan to the quack&amp;#8217;s family for an unlimited supply of nice paper.&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-right wp-block-paragraph"&gt;(&lt;a href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/14-16-girls-night-out/"&gt;Next Chapter&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="wp-block-paragraph"&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div id="jp-post-flair" class="sharedaddy sd-like-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-official sd-sharing"&gt;&lt;h3 class="sd-title"&gt;Share this:&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="sd-content"&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="share-facebook"&gt;&lt;div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/14-15-letters/" data-layout="button_count"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="share-end"&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class='sharedaddy sd-block sd-like jetpack-likes-widget-wrapper jetpack-likes-widget-unloaded' id='like-post-wrapper-130534757-5188-6a467fbeef04a' data-src='//widgets.wp.com/likes/index.html?ver=20260702#blog_id=130534757&amp;amp;post_id=5188&amp;amp;origin=shikarito.wordpress.com&amp;amp;obj_id=130534757-5188-6a467fbeef04a' data-name='like-post-frame-130534757-5188-6a467fbeef04a' data-title='Like or Reblog'&gt;&lt;div class='likes-widget-